mixin renderProductBlurbs()
  div(class='blurb__container')
    div(class='blurb__item')
      a(class='blurb__link-group' href='/mesosphere/dcos')
        h3(class='blurb__header') Mesosphere DC/OS
        div(class='blurb__desc__wrapper')
          p(class='blurb__desc') DC/OS is a distributed operating system based on the Apache Mesos distributed systems kernel. It lets you manage multiple machines as if they were a single computer. It automates resource management, schedules process placement, facilitates inter-process communication, and simplifies the installation and management of distributed services. Its included web interface and available command-line interface (CLI) facilitate remote management and monitoring of the cluster and its services.
      ul(class="blurb__links")
        for folder in latestDcosDocs.children.slice(0,4)
          li(class="blurb__link")
            a(href=folder.path)!= folder.title
    div(class='blurb__item')
      a(class='blurb__link-group' href='/ksphere/konvoy')
        h3(class='blurb__header') Konvoy
        div(class='blurb__desc__wrapper')
          p(class='blurb__desc') Developed to address the exploding demand for Kubernetes, D2iQ’s Konvoy is a unique Kubernetes distribution designed to enable companies to leverage Kubernetes for an easy, enterprise-grade experience. In addition to providing a simplified install of Kubernetes, D2iQ’s product and engineering teams did the difficult work for you by providing an opinionated set of supporting services from the vast cloud-native landscape and integrating them for an out-of-the-box, production-ready experience.  The result is a significant reduction in the man-power involved in standing up a production-ready Kubernetes environment and an accelerated time-to-market for your application development needs. 
      ul(class="blurb__links")
        for folder in latestKonvoyDocs.children.slice(0,4)
          li(class="blurb__link")
            a(href=folder.path)!= folder.title
    div(class='blurb__item')
      a(class='blurb__link-group' href='/ksphere/kommander')
        h3(class='blurb__header') Kommander
        div(class='blurb__desc__wrapper')
          p(class='blurb__desc') Kommander is an administrative cluster for multi-cluster management of Kubernetes lifecycle, governance and workloads.
      ul(class="blurb__links")
        for folder in latestKommDocs.children.slice(0,4)
          li(class="blurb__link")
            a(href=folder.path)!= folder.title
    div(class='blurb__item')
      a(class='blurb__link-group' href='/ksphere/dispatch')
        h3(class='blurb__header') Dispatch
        div(class='blurb__desc__wrapper')
          p(class='blurb__desc') Dispatch is a cloud-native GitOps platform. GitOps is a way to do Kubernetes cluster management and application delivery; it works by using Git as a single source of truth for declarative infrastructure and applications.
      ul(class="blurb__links")
        for folder in latestDispatchDocs.children.slice(0,4)
          li(class="blurb__link")
            a(href=folder.path)!= folder.title

